WEBVTT

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:02.480
that could not even reach
the opposite riverbank.

00:06:04.200 --> 00:06:06.976
Hitler's troops marched on,

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:09.920
and there was nothing
my father could do about it.

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:14.336
Until the day my father died,

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:17.720
he was frustrated
about missing these shots.

00:06:19.080 --> 00:06:20.640
He could have done something.

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:23.416
But with an old gun,

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:26.336
not even the best marksman
in the armed forces

00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:27.640
could have hit the mark.

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:31.680
So this story stayed with me.